div.d.u How do you sign up?
+br
div.d To sign up and write stories for #{firstName} and other friends, copy Harry's info below, including his friends' emails. Then reply to this email, paste that info in and change them to your own details.
+br
div.d We'll get in touch with every email address that you give us, inviting your friends to read your Sunday stories, and to write stories themselves. We've put the email address for #{firstName} in there so they'll receive your stories in return but you can take it out if you'd prefer.
+br
div.d (By the way &mdash; if you only want to receive stories from #{firstName}, and don't want to write stories yourself, you don't have to do anything at all.)
+br
div.d.i.u First name: 
