+br
div.d Lastly &mdash; if you don't want to receive stories from #{firstName}, and want us to take you off Sunday completely, just reply saying ‘NOTHANKS' and we'll delete your email from our system.
+br
div.d We hope you enjoy writing and reading stories, and that Sunday adds something to your life!
+br
div.d Yours,
div.d Sunday
